---
import MarketingLayout from "~/layouts/MarketingLayout.astro";
---
<MarketingLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | Brisbane TVs"
  description="How Brisbane TVs collects, uses and protects customer information for quotes, bookings and TV installation enquiries."
  canonical="https://brisbanetvs.com/privacy/"
  bodyClass="page-legal"
>
  <main class="legal-page">
    <div class="legal-wrap">
      <p class="legal-eyebrow">Brisbane TVs</p>
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="legal-intro">We collect only the information needed to quote, book and complete TV mounting, cable concealment, soundbar and related installation work across Greater Brisbane.</p>
      <article class="legal-card">
        <h2>Information we collect</h2>
        <p>When you request a quote or contact Brisbane TVs, we may collect your name, phone number, email address, suburb, service details, photos you send us, and notes about the wall, TV, bracket or access requirements.</p>
        <h2>How we use it</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>To respond to enquiries and provide fixed-price quotes.</li>
          <li>To schedule bookings and confirm arrival windows.</li>
          <li>To complete installation work safely and correctly.</li>
          <li>To follow up on workmanship, warranty or support questions.</li>
        </ul>
        <h2>Sharing</h2>
        <p>We do not sell customer information. We only share details where required to deliver the service, such as with a licensed electrician when electrical work is needed, or where legally required.</p>
        <h2>Storage and security</h2>
        <p>Customer messages, booking notes and quote details are kept in business systems used by Brisbane TVs. We take reasonable steps to protect this information from misuse, loss and unauthorised access.</p>
        <h2>Access and correction</h2>
        <p>You can ask us to update or remove your contact details from our active booking records, subject to any records we need to keep for business, warranty, tax or legal reasons.</p>
        <p class="legal-contact">Questions: call <a href="tel:0432145101">0432 145 101</a> or email <a href="mailto:admin@brisbanetvs.com">admin@brisbanetvs.com</a>.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </main>
</MarketingLayout>
<style>
  .legal-page { padding: 7rem 0 4rem; background: #f7f5f0; color: #151515; }
  .legal-wrap { width: min(900px, calc(100% - 2rem)); margin: 0 auto; }
  .legal-eyebrow { text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .12em; font-size: .78rem; color: #8b6f47; margin: 0 0 1rem; }
  .legal-page h1 { font-size: clamp(2.3rem, 5vw, 4.8rem); line-height: .98; margin: 0 0 1.5rem; font-family: var(--font-display, Georgia, serif); }
  .legal-intro { font-size: 1.12rem; line-height: 1.7; color: #4f4a43; max-width: 760px; margin-bottom: 2.25rem; }
  .legal-card { background: #fff; border: 1px solid #e5ded2; border-radius: 8px; padding: clamp(1.25rem, 3vw, 2rem); box-shadow: 0 18px 45px rgba(30,24,16,.07); }
  .legal-card h2 { font-size: 1.25rem; margin: 1.75rem 0 .65rem; }
  .legal-card h2:first-child { margin-top: 0; }
  .legal-card p, .legal-card li { line-height: 1.72; color: #4b4740; }
  .legal-card ul { padding-left: 1.2rem; }
  .legal-contact { margin-top: 2rem; padding-top: 1.25rem; border-top: 1px solid #ece5d8; }
</style>
